            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-concierge-bell\"></i>\n                    <h3>Personalized Service</h3>\n                    <p>Our dedicated staff ensures every need is met with impeccable attention.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"gallery\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>A Glimpse of Paradise</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery-grid\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582719478250-c89cae4dc85b?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=MnwzNjUyOXwwfDF8cmFuZG9tfHx8fHx8fHx8fDE2NzgwODkxMjQ&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&q=80&w=400\" alt=\"Luxury Suite\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073781342-f1a5726b796d?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=MnwzNjUyOXwwfDF8cmFuZG9tfHx8fHx8fHx8fDE2NzgwODkxODk&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&q=80&w=400\" alt=\"Infinity Pool\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519751113158-8675c76c1f19?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=MnwzNjUyOXwwfDF8cmFuZG9tfHx8fHx8fHx8fDE2NzgwODkyMTY&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&q=80&w=400\" alt=\"Fine Dining Restaurant\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520452879449-71f4681d7634?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=MnwzNjUyOXwwfDF8cmFuZG9tfHx8fHx8fHx8fDE2NzgwODkyNDk&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&q=80&w=400\" alt=\"Mountain View\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>For inquiries or to make a reservation, please reach out to us.</p>\n          